## ğŸ§ª Task 2: Configure Tenant-Wide MFA

Configured tenant-wide Multi-Factor Authentication to strengthen sign-in security.

Actions performed:

* Enabled MFA for all users
* Allowed Microsoft Authenticator as the primary method
* Enabled fraud alerts
* Disabled remembered MFA on trusted devices

