## ğŸ§ª Task 3: Configure Authentication Methods Policy

Configured and enabled authentication methods to support secure and flexible user authentication.

Actions performed:

* Enabled Microsoft Authenticator
* Enabled Temporary Access Pass (TAP) for onboarding and recovery
* Enabled Email OTP for guest access
* Scoped policy to all users or a designated test group

